OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1779793371
OL,3,CReform MP backs Makerfield candidate
OL,4,Cover old social media posts
OL,6,FA Reform MP has admitted social media
OL,7,Fposts by the party's by-election
OL,8,Fcandidate in Makerfield were
OL,9,F"inappropriate" but defended them as
OL,10,Fthe "private" comments of an
OL,11,F"ordinary" man.
OL,13,FPlumber Robert Kenyon, Reform's
OL,14,Fcandidate in the 18 June poll, used a
OL,15,Fnow-deleted account on X to support an
OL,16,Foffensive post about the TV presenter
OL,17,FCarol Vorderman.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
