PN,39902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1779793371
OL,3,CReform MP backs Makerfield candidate
OL,4,Cover old social media posts
OL,6,FThe campaign group Hope Not Hate
OL,7,Frevealed Mr Kenyon had responded on
OL,8,FChristmas Eve 2021 to another person's
OL,9,Fpost including graphic sexual language
OL,10,Fabout the former Countdown presenter.
OL,12,FPosting a thumbs up and a laughing
OL,13,Femoji, the plumber also wrote: "He's
OL,14,Fonly saying what we're all thinking."
OL,16,FAsked about the message, Reform MP
OL,17,FDanny Kruger told BBC Radio 4's Today
OL,18,Fprogramme: "The great challenge for
OL,19,Fsocial media for private people is
OL,20,Fthat they use it as if they are
OL,21,Fchatting to their friends in the park.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1779793371
OL,3,CReform MP backs Makerfield candidate
OL,4,Cover old social media posts
OL,6,F"Clearly an inappropriate thing to say
OL,7,Fpublicly.
OL,9,F"I'm not going to judge people for
OL,10,Ftheir what are essentially regarded at
OL,11,Fthe time and intended as private
OL,12,Fconversations."
OL,14,FIt was put to Mr Kruger that Vorderman
OL,15,Fhas described Mr Kenyon as a "cowardly
OL,16,Fmisogynist".
OL,18,FMr Kruger said: "This was clearly
OL,19,Fsomething said in a different context,
OL,20,Fnot an appropriate thing to say
OL,21,Fpublicly."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1779793371
OL,3,CReform MP backs Makerfield candidate
OL,4,Cover old social media posts
OL,6,FAsked whether Reform should drop Mr
OL,7,FKenyon as its candidate, Mr Kruger
OL,8,Fsaid: "It is clearly wrong for
OL,9,Fpoliticians to talk in that way.
OL,11,F"He was not a politician at the time.
OL,12,FHe was an ordinary man from an
OL,13,Fordinary place, and what he's done now
OL,14,Fis to step forward, outraged at the
OL,15,Fstate of our country.
OL,17,F"I'm not going to defend those
OL,18,Fcomments, but please can you
OL,19,Facknowledge that there are other
OL,20,Fconcerns at play here."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
