OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1779793371
OL,3,CReform MP backs Makerfield candidate
OL,4,Cover old social media posts
OL,6,FReform UK says it has no plans to
OL,7,Finvestigate Mr Kenyon's past social
OL,8,Fmedia use, which first sparked
OL,9,Fconcerns after he was announced as the
OL,10,Fparty's candidate for the by-election.
OL,12,FLabour Press wrote on X: "Reform:
OL,13,FRobert Kenyon's comments are
OL,14,Fcompletely unacceptable but we still
OL,15,Fwant him to be your MP..."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/5
